		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm not sure what you mean exactly. That error looks like you don't have a file by the name of "test.chr". If you don't have a file named that, you have to create one in YY-CHR or any tile editor that supports NES graphics format. And it has to be 8k. I don't know if that's what you're wondering about.

		

